Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 14:12:53 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 01/11] fix(browser): centralize url_is_file_scheme for the
 file:// gate

The file:// scheme detector backing the --allow-file-access gate lived only in obscura-cdp (pub(crate)). Move it into obscura-browser (which owns BrowserContext::allow_file_access) and re-export it from obscura-cdp's util, so the CDP and MCP navigation surfaces enforce the gate on identical logic and cannot drift (GHSA-q55h-vfv9-qcr5).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>

